{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/logwriterfunc"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Writer function for log entries. A log entry is a collection of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"GLogFields","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", using the standard "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/www.freedesktop.org\/software\/systemd\/man\/systemd.journal-fields.html","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_log_structured()"},{"text":" for more information.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/LogWriterFunc"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"typealias","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"LogWriterFunc","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" = ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GLogWriterFunc","text":"GLogWriterFunc","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Writer functions must ignore fields which they do not recognise, unless they","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can write arbitrary binary output, as field values may be arbitrary binary."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"logLevel","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is guaranteed to be included in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fields"},{"text":" as the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PRIORITY"},{"text":" field,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"but is provided separately for convenience of deciding whether or where to","type":"tex